    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Style and culture of the African ethnic group of the same name inhabiting primarily Borno state in northeastern Nigeria and in adjacent areas of Niger.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
